"548","<TEXT>"
"549","December 23, 2014"
"550","Securities and Exchange Commission"
"551","Washington, D.C. 20549"
"552","Ladies and Gentlemen:"
"553","We were previously principal accountants"
"554","for HSBC Funds, HSBC Portfolios and HSBC"
"555","Advisor Funds Trust (the Funds) and, under"
"556","the date of December 23, 2014, we"
"557","reported on the financial statements of"
"558","the Funds as of and for the years ended"
"559","October 31, 2014 and 2013. On"
"560","December 16, 2014, we were dismissed."
"561","We have read the Funds statements"
"562","included under Sub-Item 77K of their"
"563","Form N-SAR for the period ended"
"564","October 31, 2014, and we agree with"
"565","such statements, except that we are not"
"566","in a position to agree or disagree with"
"567","the Funds statement that the change"
"568","was approved by the Board of Trustees"
"569","and we are not in a position to agree or"
"570","disagree with the Funds statement that"
"571","PricewaterhouseCoopers LLP were not"
"572","engaged regarding the application of"
"573","accounting principles to a specified"
"574","transaction or the type of audit"
"575","opinion that might be rendered on the"
"576","Funds financial statements."
"577","Very truly yours,"
"578","/s/ KPMG LLP"
"579","</TEXT>"
